    <item>
      <title>世界上规模最大的选举是对莫迪对印度控制力的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/a-guide-to-india-s-six-week-election-that-will-test-modi-s-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近十亿人将前往世界上最大的民主国家投票，那里蓬勃发展的经济可能有利于总理及其执政的印度人民党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/a-guide-to-india-s-six-week-election-that-will-test-modi-s-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗告诉联合国，如果以色列停止“冒险主义”，伊朗准备降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗外交部长侯赛因·阿米拉卜杜拉希安在联合国表示，只要伊朗同意停止针对德黑兰利益的进一步军事行动，伊朗准备缓和与以色列的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:20:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
